{"type":"message","id":"b301c5f3","parentId":"daf1c0fd","timestamp":"2026-05-15T08:31:32.531Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Unity license is invalid. The error is: \"Cannot load ULF license: The digital signature is invalid., Token not found in cache\" and \"License is not active (com.unity.editor.headless)\".\n\nThe issue is that the headless (batchmode) license entitlement has expired or the ULF license file is corrupted/invalid. This needs a proper license activation.\n\nLet me check if Unity Hub has a valid license that can be activated.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_AEgw928HI95H3fwJZ09z2365","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check existing license files\nGet-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\AppData\\Roaming\\Unity\\*\" -Include \"*.ulf\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Name, Length, LastWriteTime; \nGet-ChildItem \"$env:USERPROFILE\\AppData\\Local\\Unity\\*\" -Include \"*.ulf\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Name, Length, LastWriteTime;\nWrite-Host \"---\"\nGet-ChildItem \"$env:PROGRAMDATA\\Unity\\*\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Name, Length, LastWriteTime"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":607,"output":269,"cacheRead":45184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46060,"cost":{"input":0.00008498,"output":0.00007532,"cacheRead":0.001265152,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001425452}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778833888519,"responseId":"56fdca74-8f95-46ca-8567-b9268477620f"}}
