{"type":"message","id":"5eef055a","parentId":"84806d3e","timestamp":"2026-05-15T08:31:39.448Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's a license file at `$env:PROGRAMDATA\\Unity\\Unity_lic.ulf` from Jan 14 2026. This is likely the Team License or serial-based license, but the headless/batchmode entitlement seems to have expired.\n\nThe error message says \"Cannot load ULF license: The digital signature is invalid.\" and \"Token not found in cache\" - this is the newer entitlement-based licensing system. The old ULF license serial/file might not work anymore for headless mode.\n\nLet me try a different approach - open Unity Hub and see if we can refresh the license, or use the Unity Hub's CLI to activate.\n\nActually, I think the real issue might be that the Unity Hub has the license but the batchmode activation is failing because the license needs to be refreshed. Let me check the Unity Hub status.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_5drjwXZ0n3zgohVOGIs27278","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check if we can use the Unity Hub license CLI\n$hubPath = \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity Hub\\Unity Hub.exe\"\nif (Test-Path $hubPath) { Write-Host \"Unity Hub found at $hubPath\" } else { Write-Host \"Unity Hub not found at $hubPath\" }\n\n# Check Unity Hub's licensing client\n$licClientPath = \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity Hub\\UnityLicensingClient_V1\\Unity.Licensing.Client.exe\"\nif (Test-Path $licClientPath) { Write-Host \"Licensing client found at $licClientPath\" } else { Write-Host \"Licensing client not found at $licClientPath\" }\n\n# Check if the bundled Unity licensing client exists\n$bundledLicPath = \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Data\\Resources\\Licensing\\Client\\Unity.Licensing.Client.exe\"\nif (Test-Path $bundledLicPath) { Write-Host \"Bundled licensing client found at $bundledLicPath\" } else { Write-Host \"Bundled licensing client not found\" }"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":160,"output":463,"cacheRead":45952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46575,"cost":{"input":0.000022400000000000002,"output":0.00012964,"cacheRead":0.001286656,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001438696}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778833893241,"responseId":"37eb7c80-d13f-4461-8cf8-ccad230cbd6c"}}
