{"type":"message","id":"11284eff","parentId":"d0bd463c","timestamp":"2026-05-15T08:32:11.714Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The ULF signature is corrupted/invalid, and I can't even return the license. The serial number-based license system seems to have a signature validation issue. \n\nThis is likely because the license has a bad signature - maybe due to time drift, system changes, or the ULF file itself being corrupted.\n\nLet me try a different approach:\n1. Deactivate all subscriptions\n2. Re-activate using the serial number\n\nThe serial was `F4-H1R5-BQNV-8DQZ-Q4V2-XXXX` from the earlier log.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_VqPGA4NcJnfIKRFOSaUn8761","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Try to return the ULF first with force, then re-activate\n& \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity Hub\\UnityLicensingClient_V1\\Unity.Licensing.Client.exe\" --return-ulf --serial \"F4-H1R5-BQNV-8DQZ-Q4V2-XXXX\" 2>&1","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":190,"output":245,"cacheRead":47872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48307,"cost":{"input":0.000026600000000000003,"output":0.0000686,"cacheRead":0.0013404159999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0014356159999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778833928145,"responseId":"d933ba60-02ed-4c1d-aa12-ffb5f5815aff"}}
