{"type":"message","id":"df69cdc9","parentId":"9abbc577","timestamp":"2026-05-15T08:32:18.135Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The license is completely corrupted/invalid. Let me try to manually remove the license file and then re-activate using the serial number.\n\nBut wait, the serial number I got from the log might not be the actual serial - it's partially redacted (F4-H1R5-BQNV-8DQZ-Q4V2-XXXX). The actual serial might be different, or the \"XXXX\" might be from the log redaction.\n\nLet me check the old log file more carefully for the full serial number.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_lJG6xYi5Wjivf6GAqNZ73756","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Find the serial number from the old log\nSelect-String -Path \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.1.log\" -Pattern \"Serial number\" -CaseSensitive:$false 2>$null\n# Also check if there's a backup or older log\nGet-ChildItem \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline*.log\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Name, Length, LastWriteTime"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":139,"output":262,"cacheRead":48256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48657,"cost":{"input":0.00001946,"output":0.00007336,"cacheRead":0.001351168,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001443988}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778833933934,"responseId":"66a76a39-c439-46b1-82fa-fedb72821bc5"}}
