{"type":"message","id":"0b7d7922","parentId":"388234b5","timestamp":"2026-05-15T08:32:35.077Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It needs credentials. Let me check if the Unity Hub has an existing session that we can use. The earlier successful runs connected to the Hub's licensing client successfully. Maybe I need to restart Unity Hub or the licensing client to refresh the connection.\n\nActually, I notice in the earlier successful run, the licensing client used was the Hub's version (PID 6764 from `C:/Program Files/Unity Hub/UnityLicensingClient_V1/Unity.Licensing.Client.exe`), and the log showed:\n```\n[Licensing::IpcConnector] Successfully connected to the License Client on channel: \"LicenseClient-yyzypublic\"\n```\n\nBut in the current failed runs, it's using the bundled version:\n```\nC:/Program Files/Unity/Hub/Editor/2020.3.49f1/Editor/Data/Resources/Licensing/Client/Unity.Licensing.Client.exe\n```\n\nThe difference is the license client being used. Let me try to start the Hub's licensing client first (which has the real session), and then run Unity.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_fIRz4RpxuDvWYglX5wY42221","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check if Unity Hub has a user session\nGet-Process -Name \"Unity Hub\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Id, StartTime, SessionId\nWrite-Host \"---\"\n# Check Running licensing client\nGet-Process -Name \"Unity.Licensing.Client\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Id, StartTime\n\nWrite-Host \"---\"\n$hubLicPath = \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity Hub\\UnityLicensingClient_V1\\Unity.Licensing.Client.exe\"\nif (Test-Path $hubLicPath) {\n    Write-Host \"Hub licensing client exists\"\n}\n$editorLicPath = \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1\\Editor\\Data\\Resources\\Licensing\\Client\\Unity.Licensing.Client.exe\"\nif (Test-Path $editorLicPath) {\n    Write-Host \"Editor bundled licensing client exists\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":67,"output":458,"cacheRead":49280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49805,"cost":{"input":0.00000938,"output":0.00012824,"cacheRead":0.00137984,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00151746}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778833948888,"responseId":"9808422c-96c2-4ef9-9fae-924258738bce"}}
