{"type":"message","id":"87d38385","parentId":"8677fdc3","timestamp":"2026-05-15T08:37:16.675Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"NOW we have a real error! \"It looks like another Unity instance is running with this project open.\" \n\nThere's another Unity instance that has the project open. The crash exit code is 1073741845 (which is 0xC0000005 + something, likely STATUS_ACCESS_VIOLATION or similar).\n\nBut earlier when I checked `Get-Process -Name \"Unity\"` there was no Unity process. Wait - let me check which process has the project open.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_UQPCl7Ri9L58QcNFXZ027818","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Find the Unity instance that has the project open\nGet-Process -Name \"Unity\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Id, StartTime, CPU, WorkingSet64, SessionId\nWrite-Host \"---\"\n# Also check for Unity Hub processes\nGet-Process -Name \"Unity Hub\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Id, StartTime\nWrite-Host \"---\"\n# Check for crash reports\nGet-ChildItem \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\Unity\\Editor\\Crashes\\*\" -Directory -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending | Select-Object -First 3 Name, LastWriteTime"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":409,"output":296,"cacheRead":68608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69313,"cost":{"input":0.000057260000000000004,"output":0.00008288,"cacheRead":0.001921024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002061164}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778834231892,"responseId":"54e181d4-da24-410c-ac27-d2143d9659c4"}}
